TROUBLESHOOTING HOWTO (step-by-step checks)
1. Permissions error modifying workflows during init:
   - Check repository secret WORKFLOW_TOKEN is defined and has workflow scope.
   - Check Actions -> General -> Workflow permissions is set to Read and write.
   - Re-run: npx @xn-intenton-z2a/agentic-lib@latest init
2. Agent fails to authenticate to Copilot SDK:
   - Verify COPILOT_GITHUB_TOKEN exists in repo secrets.
   - Ensure token is fine-grained and includes Copilot Read permission.
   - Inspect workflow logs for 401/403 errors.
3. Tests failing in CI only:
   - Confirm Node version in CI is >=24.0.0.
   - Check that dependencies are installed and that lockfile is respected.

